OL,3,CPort Vale reach FA Cup quarter-finals
OL,4,Cfor first time in 72-years
OL,6,FLiverpool, Manchester City, and
OL,7,FArsenal are now all potential
OL,8,Fopponents, but Brady insisted he was
OL,9,Fgiving no thought to the draw as he
OL,10,Ffocuses on trying to get out of
OL,11,Ftrouble.
OL,13,FDespite an uptick in form since Brady
OL,14,Freplaced Darren Moore in early
OL,15,FJanuary, Vale remain rooted to the
OL,16,Fbottom of League One, 11 points from
OL,17,Fsafety, and could arguably do without
OL,18,Ffurther distractions as they fight for
OL,19,Ftheir lives at the foot of the
OL,20,Fdivision, yet performances like
OL,21,FSunday's also offer belief.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
