OL,3,CPort Vale reach FA Cup quarter-finals
OL,4,Cfor first time in 72-years
OL,6,F"I wouldn't have a clue because I'm
OL,7,Fthinking about Bradford on Wednesday,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,FWaine has now hit the winner in three
OL,11,Fof Vale's FA Cup ties this season,
OL,12,Fscoring in extra time of Tuesday
OL,13,Fnight's fourth-round victory over
OL,14,FBristol City as well as an earlier tie.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]
