PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773076274
OL,3,CPort Vale reach FA Cup quarter-finals
OL,4,Cfor first time in 72-years
OL,6,FBut for a boyhood Newcastle fan to do
OL,7,Fit in a match against Sunderland was
OL,8,Fsomething extra special ` with the 24-
OL,9,Fyear-old almost lost for words when
OL,10,Fshown that Alan Shearer had retweeted
OL,11,Fan image of Waine mimicking his
OL,12,Ftrademark celebration.
OL,14,FWaine grew up in Wellington but his
OL,15,Fmum's family hail from the north east,
OL,16,Fand this was a special occasion.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
