PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773076274
OL,3,CPort Vale reach FA Cup quarter-finals
OL,4,Cfor first time in 72-years
OL,6,F"I always watched the Newcastle games
OL,7,Fagainst Sunderland and to be involved
OL,8,Fin this game and to score the winner
OL,9,Fis pretty special," Waine said. "Not
OL,10,Fjust for me, but the whole
OL,11,Ffamily...this is the dream, so you've
OL,12,Fgot to enjoy living it."
